<div id="descriptionContainer">
  
      <div id="description" class="readable stacked" style="right:0">
        
<span id="freeTextContainer15101876604576561982"><i>The Tale of the Heike</i> is one of the masterworks of Japanese literature, ranking with <i>The Tale of Genji</i> in quality and prestige. This new translation is not only far more readable than earlier ones, it is also much more faithful to the content and style of the original. Intended for the general audience as well as the specialist, this edition is highly annotated.<br/><br/></span>

